{{Top|leg}}
The '''Newcomers''' were one of the three major social groups of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]], the others being the [[Oldtimer]]s and [[Latecomer]]s. The Newcomers were the descendants of the settlers who arrived on the planet after the last [[Standard century/Legends|century]] sometime in [[44 ABY]].

